race.description: A-Plus Contracting & Poly Welding Mdn Plate
race.comment: HO ALOHA (9) race fitness should see her prove too good for these from the good draw. Cruised across from the wide barrier when a tenacious on pace second over 1200m at Kembla Grange. No excuses today. FEDERAL RESERVE (4) Justify gelding expected to have strengthened over the break. Fitted with the two trials and regular rider sticks. Look for him late. SNOWSLIDE (12) Headwater filly from a Red Ransom mare on debut for the Matthew Smith stable. Much better effort at her second trial and the lugging bit goes on from the good gate. BIFURCATION (7) trialled before racing and then overcame difficulties in running to finish third on debut over 1000m at Hawkesbury. Will take valuable race experience from that outing and is worth consideration here.
